i\" />"},{"pid":"9955a00331a08d5d64674129fde04b150695adcc","tid":50581,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"成撚日話勇武 其實差佬未撚驚過你"},{"pid":"6bbdb6abda1e77a9ac22ab747ef0012368d8365b","tid":50581,"uid":14441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"黃洋達我屌你老母"},{"pid":"4a9357bb84eadbce9ca7642a0297ae22d7bbf863","tid":50581,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"Admin 召喚"},{"pid":"6dc597777b06285087c7e1636e35a2601b0e3744","tid":50581,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗有膽組織熱血少年軍，冇一個政團有佢地既勇氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/50887?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/50887?ref=ios</a></blockquote><br />\n講起邪教又要加多一點：<br />\n邪教組織一向都係基於一啲本身已經受歡迎嘅理念，引人入局的。<br />\n<br />\n太平天國抄基督教，義和拳抄道教同傳統中國迷信野，法輪功抄new age，熱狗就抄烏克蘭中東嘅抗爭組織；以及引用陳雲嘅道教野。<br />\n<br />\n所謂健身強體練武術，要打贏差佬，佔領期間已經有人講，已經有人喺旺角街頭教，附近有拳館免費教人。<br />\n城邦派講到係自己發明嘅自製盾牌，其實係羊子學NIP友的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於熱血少年軍，即係教後生仔操fit，我早過黃洋達三個月已經喺高登開post討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6106191&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6106191%26page%3D1&d=m6%2BIrinw8%2B9tR7N%2FW6xkEJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=6fa5e868\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6106191&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"e00e69b71fcc8963080366689d95ab8f68a285d5","tid":50581,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"義和團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d955e1e4053361a67cc27a246c6b0fcc869c9381","tid":50581,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"話之你地狗咬狗.<br />\n唔好搞亂時事台..<br />\n去政事台 la..."},{"pid":"21d8baf3e962e248bc723a572a1498a7d0c90403","tid":50581,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>義和團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法術神功護體 &gt; 陳雲召喚大鵬金翅鳥<br />\n義和拳 &gt; 運動救世<br />\n反清復明 &gt; 光復華夏<br />\n拳匪 &gt; 熱匪"},{"pid":"2946752431b9d336990f991ce176cff1da9db322","tid":50581,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話之你地狗咬狗.<br />\n唔好搞亂時事台..<br />\n去政事台 la...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實而家係仔細分析討論邪教 真係冇乜提政治喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac3f822b8fe070c01940123c221e02ea6f5ace9","tid":50581,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:37:45.000Z","msg":"站務台開post即做野<br />\nho ball"},{"pid":"a98bd734d538d5a40b61cf8300ce65e41ebde559","tid":50581,"uid":57394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0c5d25abddb86a42287022321c0fe3ed13ca1a5","tid":50581,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一鍵留名"},{"pid":"b924234860da4fddcdcd08246e139fe3a731d0b8","tid":50581,"uid":30203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0cbbc48a39597f48ecc0846fe90799e7d4219e","tid":50581,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>站務台開post即做野<br />\nho ball</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇住隻熱狗有時屌有時求admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知仲以為精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66426bac32b79fea008a6bf3f5bbd3815e2d882a","tid":50581,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法輪功係撚邪教<br />\n法輪功只係一d 太極養生嘅運動，只係支那大多人練，共狗政府怕法輪功太團結一齊反佢先屈佢地係邪教。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本邏輯你都唔撚識<br />\n共狗話好嘅姐係唔好<br />\n唔好姐係好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有個uncle(老豆舊同事) 十幾年前信左法輪功<br />\n離婚跟埋李洪志去外國之後失咗蹤 佢走之前每個月捐大部份薪水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邪教都可以反共 唔好非黑則白OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝你把網上討論導正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785fa3529d92d11586b42a9015e3fe88ba6a9672","tid":50581,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有個uncle(老豆舊同事) 十幾年前信左法輪功<br />\n離婚跟埋李洪志去外國之後失咗蹤 佢走之前每個月捐大部份薪水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邪教都可以反共 唔好非黑則白OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢番左大陸包二奶。<br />\n<br />\n我對法輪功無研究<br />\n我一直都以為係法輪功係邪教<br />\n最近睇左本書講propaganda ，先回想法輪功都可能係共狗其中一個宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n大約97~99 因為太多人練功，肛澤文出力打壓並開始對宣揚佢地係邪教。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過法輪功全世界都周圍擺檔，財政方面的確幾令人懷疑。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝您把網上討論導正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a094e1471dcea8698f5465fecb493d531aa89354","tid":50581,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"有無熱狗可以反證熱血公民唔係邪教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2f1ff37fff4f29405be9029371a4005c1caa08","tid":50581,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無熱狗可以反證熱血公民